    "Therefore, it is necessary to develop a new large-scale polyp segmentation dataset to serve as a baseline for future research.",
    "In addition, collecting datasets for complex specialized scenarios is also a potential direction.",
    "For example, constructing multi-center datasets, multitarget datasets, and specialized datasets for small or large polyps could enhance the model's performance in different scenarios.",
